title: The Ink Spots Greatest Hits [V0](Big Papi) 40's Vocal Pop
description:
Source: CD


Big Papi has a vinyl rip of Spotlight if you're into some original vinyl with occasional clicks and pops. The Donuts song is so cool.

This sort of music is widely used in video games and serial killer movies for some reason. Perhaps it is about the most contrast one can get between pure innocence and dastardly deeds.

- Big Papi
